&gt;&gt; From the Library of
Congress in Washington, DC.

00:00:03.510 --> 00:00:21.600
[ Silence ]

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:23.470
&gt;&gt; I'd like to introduce
Chris Germain,

00:00:23.470 --> 00:00:28.390
director of the Oberlin
Violinmakers Workshop.

00:00:28.390 --> 00:00:29.690
&gt;&gt; Thank you.

00:00:29.690 --> 00:00:31.910
Good evening, everybody,
and welcome.

00:00:31.910 --> 00:00:33.480
Really happy to be here.

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:35.500
And before we get into
the program tonight,

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:38.820
I'd like to just give a word
of thanks to everyone here

00:00:38.820 --> 00:00:40.910
at the library of [tape
skips] absolutely wonderful

00:00:40.910 --> 00:00:42.780
to work with, and so supportive.

