00:00:48.820 --> 00:00:52.550
without their total help.

00:00:52.550 --> 00:00:54.140
And that's what we're
going to do tonight.

00:00:54.140 --> 00:00:56.440
We want to tell you
what I think is going

00:00:56.440 --> 00:01:00.470
to be a really interesting story
that's going to span 300 years

00:01:00.470 --> 00:01:04.270
about violins, starting
with Antonio Stradivari,

00:01:04.270 --> 00:01:06.890
and leading up the modern day.

00:01:06.890 --> 00:01:08.980
But before we begin
to tell you the story,

00:01:08.980 --> 00:01:13.140
I would like to have the musical
performance of the two violins,

00:01:13.140 --> 00:01:15.940
the original Betts Stradivari,
which is in the collection here

00:01:15.940 --> 00:01:20.050
