copy that we made at our workshop

00:01:20.050 --> 00:01:22.300
at the BSA Overland Workshop.

00:01:22.300 --> 00:01:25.970
And to do that, I would like to
introduce two very fine violinists,

00:01:25.970 --> 00:01:29.220
some friends, Claudia Chudacoff

00:01:29.220 --> 00:01:32.510
and Christopher Franke,
please, both members --

00:01:32.510 --> 00:01:37.580
