[ Silence ]

00:04:28.510 --> 00:06:52.510
[ Violins Play ]

00:06:52.510 --> 00:07:03.180
[ Applause ]

00:07:03.180 --> 00:07:07.380
&gt;&gt; So this was a chance to hear the
